			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div><a href="http://www.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/americas/03/05/canada.bus.beheading/index.html" target="_blank">Judge rules bus beheading suspect mentally ill</a><br />
<br />
<div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px; ">
	<div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px">Quote:</div>
	<table cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
